!     UPDATED         --JUNE      1998. SOME NEW MATRIX COMMANDS
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST    1998. MATRIX MEAN
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST    1998. MATRIX ADD ROW, MATRIX DELE ROW
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST    1998. DISTANCE FROM MEAN
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST    1998. FOR MATRIX COMMANDS, FIX HOW
!                                       SUBSETTING HANDLED WHEN OUTPUT
!                                       IS SAVED.  THE IUPFLG USED TO
