!                                       CALL LIST TO MATAR3)
!     UPDATED         --MARCH     2006. MATRIX LOWER TRUNCATE
!     UPDATED         --MARCH     2006. MATRIX UPPER TRUNCATE
!     UPDATED         --OCTOBER   2007. COMOVEMENT MATRIX
!     UPDATED         --APRIL     2008. MINIMAL SPANNING TREE
!     UPDATED         --JUNE      2008. MATRIX RENUMBER
