!     UPDATED         --JUNE      2012. CORRELATION CDF MATRIX
!     UPDATED         --JUNE      2012. CORRELATION PVALUE MATRIX
!     UPDATED         --AUGUST    2017. GENERATE MATRIX <STAT>
